Question 77 Let A be a square matrix size n x n. Consider the following pseudocode. What is the
expected output? C = 100;
for i = 1 to n do
   for j = 1 to n do
   {
      Temp = A[ i ] [ j ] + C ;
      A [ i ] [ j ] = A [ j ] [ i ] ;
      A [ j ] [ i ] = Temp - C ;
   }
for i = 1 to n do
    for j = 1 to n do
         output (A[ i ] [ j ]);
